<LanguageData>

	<!-- EN: Atomic Cellular Regeneration -->
	<AtomicCellularRegeneration.label>原子细胞再生</AtomicCellularRegeneration.label>

	<!-- EN: Allows the construction of MedPods, advanced hospital beds capable of automatically treating a wide range of diseases and injuries by rapidly repairing living cells on an atomic level. -->
	<AtomicCellularRegeneration.description>让你可以建造智能医疗床，采用原子再生技术来自动快速修复细胞，治疗多种疾病和伤势。</AtomicCellularRegeneration.description>

	<!-- EN: About: Building MedPods -->
	<AtomicCellularRegeneration.discoveredLetterTitle>关于：建造智能医疗床</AtomicCellularRegeneration.discoveredLetterTitle>

	<!-- EN: You now have the technology to build MedPod beds - but each MedPod requires a special Isolinear Processor component. You can collect Isolinear Processors several ways:\n\n -Orbital or caravan exotic goods traders sell Isolinear Processors. Invite or wait for them.\n -Some quests are rewarded with Isolinear Processors.\n -Disassemble an AI persona core to extract Isolinear Processors (along with various other components). -->
	<AtomicCellularRegeneration.discoveredLetterText>现在你可以建造智能医疗床了，但每张智能医疗床需要一个等线性处理器零件来建造。你可以透过以下几种方式收集等线性处理器：\n\n -外贸轨道商人或拜访的外贸贸易旅队有时候会卖等线性处理器。邀请或等待他们拜访。 \n -有些任务会有等线性处理器作为奖励。 \n -拆解一个AI人格核心，以获取等线性处理器(与其他有用的零件)。 </AtomicCellularRegeneration.discoveredLetterText>
	
</LanguageData>